{"tid":1397054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"算有嚴重嘅情緒病 你問我答","createTime":"2019-08-02T10:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:50:42.000Z","uid":18648,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"198fef865c53f982db9d16850a25024cf3e9227e","tid":1397054,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"香港嘅近況最近令好多手足壓力爆煲<br />\n小弟好擔心手足諱疾忌醫<br />\n令個病變到嚴重 甚至輕生<br />\n所以小弟想問個po講下睇精神科嘅經歷<br />\n<br />\n中度至嚴重抑鬱<br />\n焦慮 強迫 專注力不足<br />\n醫咗年半<br />\n屋企尚算比得起錢我睇醫生<br />\n同醫生經濟上幫到我好多<br />\n<br />\n手足 有情緒問題唔好怕<br />\n都市病好多人都有<br />\n唔好比自己覺得孤單<br />\n有需要嘅就搵人傾<br />\n唔好收埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頂唔順就真係要搵醫生睇<br />\n錢可以再搵 失去健康多多錢都洗得唔開心<br />\n<br />\nP.s唔好問我睇邊個醫生<br />\n廢撚事比人話我係打手"},{"pid":"d4f3709739b286f761e399722e10700b4a25e0a5","tid":1397054,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"患病源頭係？"},{"pid":"7b029527f940924cc850d1389ab5a4b7d3bb7261","tid":1397054,"uid":18648,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d4f3709739b286f761e399722e10700b4a25e0a5","tid":1397054,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"患病源頭係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:08:06.000Z","msg":"前女友 成日搵佢個ex <br />\n逼撚爆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7642a6e5d2495a5e3d34bc0bf6f30f535d009d64","tid":1397054,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"睇私家？"},{"pid":"1566a9cc20b3a29f7bb7a3a043a6c7eb1e7f088c","tid":1397054,"uid":18648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7642a6e5d2495a5e3d34bc0bf6f30f535d009d64","tid":1397054,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"睇私家？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"係 公立嘅藥好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"cb4f705c16b6b330f3bdaec0733ca7c0aa38ac29","tid":1397054,"uid"